OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FEducation Minister Paul Givan and
OL,8,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt have
OL,9,Fapologised for the distress caused by
OL,10,Fan announcement that special school
OL,11,Fsummer schemes would not go ahead this
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FMLAs told a recalled Assembly that the
OL,15,FU-turn on the withdrawal of summer
OL,16,Fschemes was emblematic of "Executive
OL,17,Fchaos", and that vulnerable children
OL,18,Fand their families should not be used
OL,19,Fas "pawns".
OL,26,@xD@[OUyD@FO]{D@DOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
