CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FMr Givan acknowledged the announcement
OL,8,Fthat the summer schemes could not go
OL,9,Fahead was "disruptive" and "difficult"
OL,10,Ffor parents and special school pupils.
OL,12,F"I regret the distress it caused and
OL,13,Fon behalf of all involved, I apologise
OL,14,Fto them," he told the Assembly.
OL,16,FHe said some politicians were looking
OL,17,Fto "exploit" the issue and accused
OL,18,FSinn Fein of "using children to pursue
OL,19,Ftheir vendetta" against Israel and
OL,20,FDonald Trump.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@VO]qD@\OUqD@fO]tD@AOUvD@IO]yD@
OL,26,ADOUyD@LO]zD@NOU{D@OO]
