OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FMr Nesbitt told the Assembly: "I want
OL,8,Fto offer an unconditional apology to
OL,9,Fthe families for the 24 hours of
OL,10,Funnecessary stress and distress."
OL,12,FThe Assembly was recalled after it
OL,13,Femerged on Thursday that the summer
OL,14,Fschemes, which provide support for
OL,15,Fchildren with additional needs during
OL,16,Fthe summer break, would not take place
OL,17,Fthis year over concerns about the
OL,18,Fhealthcare available for pupils.
OL,26,@oD@_OUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FThe Education Authority (EA) said
OL,8,Fnursing-led support was needed at the
OL,9,Fschemes and would not be provided,
OL,10,Fwhile the Department of Health said
OL,11,Fonsite registered nursing provision
OL,12,Fwas not needed at all sites.
OL,14,FAfter public and political backlash,
OL,15,Fthe EA announced 24 hours later that
OL,16,Fthe summer schemes would go ahead.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
