PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FThe Department of Health said it would
OL,8,Fprovide nursing support at each summer
OL,9,Fscheme site after discussions between
OL,10,Fthe EA and the departments of
OL,11,Feducation and health.
OL,13,FMr Givan credited the intervention of
OL,14,FMr Nesbitt after he directed "his
OL,15,Fofficials for the correct outcome to
OL,16,Fbe delivered after months of
OL,17,Fengagements with health officials".
OL,26,@vD@^OUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
