OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FSpeaking in the Assembly on Tuesday,
OL,8,FAlliance deputy leader Eoin Tennyson
OL,9,Fsaid "to pull the rug" on the schemes
OL,10,Fwas "an appalling dereliction of duty"
OL,11,Fby Mr Nesbitt and Mr Givan.
OL,13,FHe said the announcement had "slipped
OL,14,Fout" just as the Assembly broke for
OL,15,Frecess "knowing full well the chaos
OL,16,Fthat would ensue for families".
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@VO]rD@EOUrD@fO]uD@^OUvD@DO]wD@
OL,26,AHOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
