OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FSinn Fein MLA Cathy Mason said the
OL,8,Fcancellation of summer schemes was
OL,9,F"nothing short of a disgrace" and it
OL,10,Fwas a "crisis of the minister's own
OL,11,Fmaking".
OL,13,FShe accused Mr Givan of "chasing pet
OL,14,Fprojects" by visiting Israel and the
OL,15,Foccupied Palestinian territories
OL,16,Frather than focusing on "the most
OL,17,Fvulnerable children here at home".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@]O]rD@GOUsD@GO]uD@YOUvD@IO]xD@
OL,26,AYOUyD@aO]
