OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FThe SDLP's Colin McGrath said the
OL,8,Fissue was "a stain on this Executive"
OL,9,Fwith ministers "blaming each other"
OL,10,Fbefore they "had to bow to public
OL,11,Fpressure".
OL,13,FTUV MLA Timothy Gaston said summer
OL,14,Fschemes for children with special
OL,15,Feducational needs "are not an optional
OL,16,Fextra".
OL,18,F"Don't try to tell me that this whole
OL,19,Fthing doesn't stink," he said.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@eO]qD@POUqD@cO]rD@MOUsD@IO]wD@
OL,26,ASOUxD@FO]zD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
