OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774976748
OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,F"The whole sorry episode boils down to
OL,8,Fnothing more than a political game,
OL,9,Fshamelessly using the most vulnerable
OL,10,Fchildren in our society and their
OL,11,Ffamilies as pawns."
OL,13,FPeople Before Profit MLA Gerry Carroll
OL,14,Fsaid the issue was "a masterclass in
OL,15,FExecutive chaos" and parents bore the
OL,16,Fweight of Mr Givan's "abject failure".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]vD@TOUwD@PO]xD@VOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
