OL,3,CGivan and Nesbitt apologise to
OL,4,Cfamilies over summer scheme U-turn
OL,5,C'distress'
OL,7,FSpeaker Edwin Poots said at the
OL,8,Fbeginning of proceedings that the
OL,9,Fissue was a serious one and the debate
OL,10,Fshould not be used "just for taking
OL,11,Flumps out of each other".
